              <li>Buka Google Drive dan buat <strong>Google Spreadsheet</strong> baru.</li>
              <li>Beri nama spreadsheet (misal: "Database Pushbike").</li>
              <li>Klik menu <strong>Extensions (Ekstensi)</strong> &gt; <strong>Apps Script</strong>.</li>
